productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
My goldfinch loves to play with it.
It only works when I'm Guernsey.
